    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "思路几乎就是 <a href=\"/p/p1450-[haoi2008]-硬币购物\" class=\"wikilink\">P1450 [HAOI2008] 硬币购物</a> 这题，一共 20 个限制条件，只不过全集需要用<strong>组合数学的隔板法</strong>计算。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "void solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tll n, s; cin >> n >> s;\n\tvar f = vector<ll>(n);\n\tfa(i, 0, n - 1)cin >> f[i];\n\n\t// 上限为 s 时，不考虑每个盒子花的数量（假设每个盒子的花上限为无穷），算总数\n\tll tot = Math::C((s + n - 1) % mod, n - 1, mod); \n\n\tll ans = 0;\n\tfa(i, 1, (1 << n) - 1) {\n\t\tll now = s;\n\t\t// 先确保状态为 1 的肯定都违规了\n\t\tfa(k, 0, n - 1)if (i & (1 << k))now -= f[k] + 1;\n\t\tif (now < 0)continue;\n\t\t// 奇加偶减法\n\t\tif (popcnt64(i) & 1)ans = (ans + Math::C((now + n - 1) % mod, n - 1, mod)) % mod;\n\t\telse ans = ((ans - Math::C((now + n - 1) % mod, n - 1, mod)) % mod + mod) % mod;\n\t}\n\tcout << ((tot - ans) % mod + mod) % mod << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
